'''FC Balzers''' is a [[Liechtenstein]]er [[football (soccer)|football]] team that plays in [[Balzers]].

Their home is the Sportplatz Rheinau which is situated right next to the Rhein close to the border with [[Tr<U+00FC>bbach]] in Switzerland.

Traditionally, FC Balzers is the second biggest football club in Liechtenstein, and play in the 2.Liga Inter-Regional (which is the 4th tier of the [[Swiss Football League]]).  [[USV Eschen/Mauren]] also play in this league.

==Achievements==
* '''[[Liechtenstein football Cup]]''': 11
:: 1964, 1973, 1979, 1981, 1982, 1983, 1984, 1989, 1991, 1993, 1997

